verbose_text: The increase in impulsivity with NAc shell stimulation may be related to changes in local neurotransmitter concentrations : NAc shell HFS also increased concentrations of NAc dopamine and serotonin, while NAc core stimulation does not in result in any local change in dopamine, serotonin, or noradrenaline concentrations.
evidence: NAc shell HFS also increased concentrations of NAc dopamine and serotonin
